<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Could Not Be Completed | Vidyari</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5576c 0%, #f093fb 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .failure-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            animation: slideUp 0.6s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes slideUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .failure-icon {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5576c 0%, #f093fb 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            animation: shake 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        .failure-icon i {
            color: white;
            font-size: 40px;
        }

        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
            25% {
                transform: translateX(-5px);
            }
            75% {
                transform: translateX(5px);
            }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .error-details {
            background: #fff5f5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f5576c;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .error-message {
            color: #c53030;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 14px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        .error-message i {
            margin-top: 2px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .error-reason {
            color: #c53030;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 13px;
            padding-top: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #fed7d7;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .btn {
            padding: 14px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: #f0f0f0;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .support-section {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .support-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .support-text {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .support-options {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .support-link {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .support-link:hover {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-color: #667eea;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .tips {
            background: #f0f7ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .tips-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .tip-item {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .tip-item i {
            color: #667eea;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .failure-container {
                padding: 40px 25px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .cta-buttons {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .support-options {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: stretch;
            }

            .support-link {
                justify-content: center;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="failure-container">
        <div class="failure-icon">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i>
        </div>

        <h1>Order Not Completed</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">
            We couldn't complete your purchase at this time. Your payment method was not charged. Please try again.
        </p>

        <div class="error-details">
            <div class="error-message">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
                <div>
                    <div>What happened?</div>
                    <div class="error-reason">
                        <% 
                            let reasonText = "Your order couldn't be completed";
                            if (reason === 'invalid') reasonText = "Invalid payment link. Please try again.";
                            else if (reason === 'file_not_found') reasonText = "The product is no longer available.";
                            else if (reason === 'not_completed') reasonText = "Payment was not completed or was cancelled.";
                            else if (reason === 'verification_error') reasonText = "A verification error occurred. Please try again.";
                        %>
                        <%= reasonText %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tips">
            <div class="tips-title"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> Try these steps</div>
            <div class="tip-item">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                <span>Ensure you have a stable internet connection</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tip-item">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                <span>Try a different payment method</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tip-item">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                <span>Contact your bank if the issue persists</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tip-item">
                <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                <span>Reach out to Vidyari Support for assistance</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <i class="fas fa-home"></i> Back to Home
            </a>
            <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-primary">
                <i class="fas fa-redo"></i> Try Again
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="support-section">
            <div class="support-title">
                <i class="fas fa-headset"></i> Vidyari Support
            </div>
            <p class="support-text">
                We're here to help! If you continue to experience issues, our support team will assist you immediately.
            </p>
            <div class="support-options">
                <a href="mailto:support@vidyari.com?subject=Payment%20Issue" class="support-link">
                    <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email
                </a>
                <a href="https://wa.me/919999999999?text=I%20am%20having%20payment%20issues" target="_blank" class="support-link">
                    <i class="fas fa-whatsapp"></i> WhatsApp
                </a>
                <a href="/contact" class="support-link">
                    <i class="fas fa-headset"></i> Live Chat
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top: 25px; color: #999; font-size: 12px;">
            Your payment information is secure and encrypted. No charges have been made to your account.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
